&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for the position of Orthopaedic Trauma Junior Fellow FY2 Grade. We have positions available to start 2nd December 2020, fixed term for 12 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We seek suitably qualified candidates to join the team at the renowned Oxford Trauma Unit. Working with us will provide a broad education in both orthopaedic trauma management, as well as in peri-operative medical management, particularly of the elderly. Although not a formal training post, the successful candidates will work the same rota as those in training, and the departmental educational opportunities will be identical&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Applicants must hold a full GMC registration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
